data.description: This home is easy to get to, with a very quiet country feel. There is plenty of room for horses, goats, and other fun farm animals. The 9ft pond is located near the easement gates in the pasture area. The covered lean-to has four stalls. perfect for grooming and shelter. The fenced in back yard with covered patio makes a Great place for grilling and entertaining friends and family. The front yard is spacious and provides many possibilities for curb side appeal. Leaf Guard filters are in the gutter system, which helps to keep them draining properly. The AC unit was recently replaced at the beginning of this summer. The interior of the home provides lots of living space. The bonus room can be utilized as an office, study, hobby room, playroom, or additional bedroom. With the kitchen and living area wide open, stools can be placed around the counter to keep the cook company. Your favorite movies or sports can be playing on your TV while everyone gets to enjoy the fun!!! COME HOME!!!
